data.name: label1.Text
data.value:
While this tracker is mainly designed for the Majoras Mask Randomizer, it can theoretically support any game so long as you provide the tracker with a logic file in the style of MMRs logic file, and a dictionary.
Dictionary and Logic Files for certain games have been included in the randomizer along with a tool that will automatically convert the spoiler log generated by that game into one readble by this tracker. The recources for these games can be found below.
NOTE: Importing a spoiler log for these games with a logic file for these games already loaded will automatically convert them. The logic files for these games can also be found in File -> Templates.
